  m_text: "Welcome to the world of Atlas Defence! Here you can challange yourself
    to protect yourself from enemies, and save yourself along with your castle!\n-
    In order to start playing, press the Single Player button.\n- In order to play
    the challange mode, press the Event button.\n- To check all of the challanges,
    press the Trophy button.\n- Feel like bying something, check the store!\n- Don't
    forget to checkout our social media so that you won't miss nay of our\n  recent
    events!"
